---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = 'OpenAI introduces workspace agents in ChatGPT for team collaboration';
const description = 'OpenAI 发布 Workspace Agents：面向团队的共享智能体。';
---

<Layout 
  title={title}
  description={description}
  type="article"
  publishedTime="2026-04-22"
  tags={["AI-Agents", "OpenAI", "ChatGPT", "Workspace", "Collaboration"]
}
>
  <article class="article-content">
    <h1 class="lang-content lang-zh active">OpenAI 发布 Workspace Agents：面向团队的共享智能体</h1>
    <h1 class="lang-content lang-en">OpenAI introduces workspace agents in ChatGPT for team collaboration</h1>
    
    <time datetime="2026-04-22">2026-04-22</time>
    
    <div class="lang-content lang-zh active">
      <p>OpenAI 推出面向团队的 Workspace Agents，支持复杂任务和长期工作流。基于 Codex 构建，可在 ChatGPT 和 Slack 中协作使用，并支持按计划触发和自动执行。</p>
      <p><a href="https://openai.com/index/introducing-workspace-agents-in-chatgpt/" target="_blank">阅读原文</a></p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="lang-content lang-en">
      <p>OpenAI introduces workspace agents in ChatGPT, enabling teams to create shared agents for complex tasks and long-running workflows. Powered by Codex, these agents can work in the cloud, integrate with Slack, and operate on schedules.</p>
      <p><a href="https://openai.com/index/introducing-workspace-agents-in-chatgpt/" target="_blank">Read the full article</a></p>
    </div>
    
    <a href="/" class="back-link">← Back to articles</a>
  </article>
</Layout>
